{"tid":1588983,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"四川學者以「習近平」命名新臭蟲　讚其領導致國家強大　被內地網站封殺","createTime":"2019-09-23T05:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T07:47:38.000Z","uid":228360,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa027d36cb4c72881d968c0b755d094d2bc61ae","tid":1588983,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"中國四川學者王成斌於6月在知名學術期刊《Zootaxa》發表論文，公布其最新發現的海南島甲蟲新品種&mdash;&mdash;「習氏狼條脊甲 Rhyzodiastes（Temoana） xii」，並以國家主席習近平來命名，指中國在習的領導下越趨強大，惟相關文章遭内地網站封殺。<br />\n<br />\n論文由四川學者王成斌博士撰寫，名為《Rhyzodiastes (Temoana) xii sp. nov. (Coleoptera: Rhysodidae: Clinidiini), a new species from Hainan Island, China 習氏狼條脊甲（鞘翅目：條脊甲科：斜條脊甲族），來自中國海南島的新物種》，於6月17日在國際知名動物學術期刊《Zootaxa》的網頁發布。條脊甲科體長4至8微米，屬小型甲蟲，身體多為黑色，頭部、前胸背板、鞘翅表面均具深溝。<br />\n<br />\n王成斌在文中提到：「這個種名是獻給中華人民共和國國家主席習近平，因在他的領導下祖國越來越強大。」該論文的消息近日被内地網民發現，隨即在内地網站廣傳。網民起初以為是惡搞，細閲後才發現真有其事。但有關消息已經遭内地網站封殺。<br />\n<br />\n記者以「習氏狼條脊甲」及「習近平臭蟲」作關鍵字搜尋，微博、新浪網及百度網站均未能顯示相關消息，其中微博指根據相關「法律法規和政策」，「習氏狼條脊甲」搜索結果未予顯示。<br />\n<br />\n過往曾有科學家以國家領導人的名字來命名新物種，其中蜘蛛Aptostichus barackobamai 以美國總統奧巴馬命名，海蛞蝓Mandelia mirocornata亦以已故南非前總統曼德拉作命名。而以中國領導人之名命名則是首例。<br />\n<br />\n話刁大大係蟲，反了反了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fabd84260e7d4316ca2dbc991b388b364a258d7","tid":1588983,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"b60446ecca3b7bcc131acce5ad24816b70463dfd","tid":1588983,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d983a34b24183b6205ed56787f5035a1bf206d","tid":1588983,"uid":228360,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwSNcXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwSNcXq.jpg&h=242d0a47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c36e4a1b3cb1e3e847e19009743808ec81010b4","tid":1588983,"uid":122134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"Rhyzodiastes（Temoana） xii<br />\n<br />\n令我諗到iphone唔敢叫iphone xi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643c3b73702eb4300823c9da5614a02ccdc212c7","tid":1588983,"uid":115238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"高級黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bdc7477d48a20a86fc1d1cee727f146b103dbe","tid":1588983,"uid":29198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"Xii讀出嚟即係屎？"},{"pid":"6a01b4c5aa9b2793797e90827168c8f5821c167b","tid":1588983,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c36e4a1b3cb1e3e847e19009743808ec81010b4","tid":1588983,"uid":122134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"Rhyzodiastes（Temoana） xii<br />\n<br />\n令我諗到iphone唔敢叫iphone xi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\niPhone XI Pro<br />\nIPhone 專業習世代，因習之名"},{"pid":"79f5fc537e1d45cdd285